(142, 'CSC', '6710', 'Database Systems', '4.0', 'CSC 3410', 'An introduction to the fundamental concepts and principles that underlie the relational model of data. Topics include formal query languages; SQL; query optimization; relational database design theory; and physical database design, integrity, security, and concurrency control.'),
